screens.screen_desc: A person is holding a small glass container with a lid in a kitchen setting. The background features a tiled backsplash and an electrical outlet. The video is 43 seconds long, and the interface shows options for liking, commenting, sharing, and more. The profile at the top indicates that the user "Marcie Dallas" earns commissions and is discussing the glass containers. There is also a small image of various colored glass containers on the right side of the screen.

flow_desc: "A user named Marcie Dallas presents a 43-second video focused on glass containers in a kitchen setting, featuring a small glass container with a lid against a stylish backdrop. Viewers can explore various options, including liking, commenting, and sharing. To engage, users are instructed to tap the heart icon, represented as a like button with 6 existing likes, encouraging interaction with the content. The right side of the screen showcases an array of colorful glass containers, enhancing the visual appeal of the video. This flow effectively blends product showcase with user engagement capabilities."
